            "stanza_text": "Le Soleil est le tout-puissant\nQui féconde, en éblouissant,\nPlaines, coteaux, monts et vallées :\nLes immensités étalées\nSous leur plafond d'azur luisant."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Il éclate retentissant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Jusqu'aux ravines désolées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Fait les terres bariolées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Rend irisé, phosphorescent,",
