                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Le dos houleux des mers gonflées.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il éclate retentissant\nJusqu'aux ravines désolées,\nFait les terres bariolées,\nRend irisé, phosphorescent,\nLe dos houleux des mers gonflées."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Il trouve tout obéissant :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Bois enfouis, roches voilées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Les eaux courantes ou gelées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et l'ombre elle-même le sent.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Il trouve tout obéissant :\nBois enfouis, roches voilées,\nLes eaux courantes ou gelées,\nEt l'ombre elle-même le sent."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Au zénith d'où vont jaillissant",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Ses lumières immaculées,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Fixe il trône ! et, quand il descend",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Dans l'air frais, par lui rougissant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Il jette aux profondeurs troublées",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Ses deux grandes pourpres mêlées :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Celle du feu, celle du sang.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Le Soleil est le tout-puissant !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Au zénith d'où vont jaillissant\nSes lumières immaculées,\nFixe il trône ! et, quand il descend\nDans l'air frais, par lui rougissant,\nIl jette aux profondeurs troublées\nSes deux grandes pourpres mêlées :\nCelle du feu, celle du sang.\nLe Soleil est le tout-puissant !"
